Pater fīlium interrogāvit 'num bonus discipulus {{c1::fuisset}}: num magistrō {{c1::pāruisset}}, attentē {{c1::audīvisset}}, rēctē {{c1::scrīpsisset}} et pulchrē {{c1::recitāvisset}}.'

Fīlius nōn respondit.

Tum pater ab eō quaesīvit 'num ā magistrō {{c2::laudātus esset}}.'

Cum fīlius id {{c3::negāvisset}}, "Ergō" inquit pater "malus discipulus fuistī; nam sī bonus discipulus {{c3::fuissēs}}, magister tē {{c3::laudāvisset}}.

Sī magistrō {{c4::pāruissēs}}, attentē {{c4::audīvissēs}}, rēctē {{c4::scrīpsissēs}} et pulchrē {{c4::recitāvissēs}}, ā magistrō {{c5::laudātus essēs}}."

Fīlius: "Etiam sī industrius {{c6::fuissem}}, magister mē nōn {{c6::laudāvisset}}."

Pater: "Quid?" Fīlius: "Etiam sī magistrō {{c8::pāruissem}}, attentē {{c8::audīvissem}}, rēctē {{c8::scrīpsissem}} et pulchrē {{c8::recitāvissem}}, {{c9::laudātus}} nōn {{c9::essem}} ab illō magistrō iniūstō!"

Pater fīliōs interrogāvit 'num bonī discipulī {{c1::fuissent}}: num magistrō {{c1::pāruissent}}, attentē {{c1::audīvissent}}, rēctē {{c1::scrīpsissent}} et pulchrē {{c1::recitāvissent}}.'

Fīliī nōn respondērunt.

Tum pater ab iīs quaesīvit 'num ā magistrō {{c5::laudātī essent.}}'

Cum fīliī id {{c2::negāvissent}}, "Ergō" inquit pater "malī discipulī fuistis; nam sī bonī discipulī {{c2::fuissētis}}, magister vōs {{c2::laudāvisset}}.

Sī magistrō {{c3::pāruissētis}}, attentē {{c3::audīvissētis}}, rēctē {{c3::scrīpsissētis}} et pulchrē {{c3::recitāvissētis}}, ā magistrō {{c5::laudātī essētis}}."

[D.:] {{c2::Positīvus}}, ut {{c3::doctus}}, {{c4::comparātīvus}}, ut {{c5::doctior}}, {{c6::su­perlātīvus}}, ut {{c7::doctissimus}}. [M.:] Quae nōmina comparantur? [M.:] Cāsus item prōnōminum quot sunt? 
[D.:] Sex, {{c1::quem ad modum et}} nōminum, per quōs omnium generum prōnōmina {{c2::īnflectuntur}} . . .

[1] {{c1::persōnālia}}: {{c2::ego, tū, nōs, vōs, sē}}

[D.:] Pars ōrātiōnis quae {{c2::praeposita}} aliīs partibus ōrāti­ōnis significātiōnem eārum aut {{c3::complet}} aut {{c4::mūtat}} aut {{c5::minuit}} ....

multa super {{c1::Priamō}} rogitāns, super {{c2::Hectore}} multa
